紧张局势的增加，它扩大了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/5tRykMqz4xs18V0lc37xWXoQargV53i1saOvcLq7EOcNX5_QHQmIBA2jaMvdQu9SHOK1Wlavq1kb4zbNcgUX2H1c_Gfy7kk2r9EMk_JhchbR5NnzrEYMz7f2Ek0D_BLv4_IFw3DdOzUFXDyypHG_28CljXyyhYUQzj-cWKQh_zuCQs4AeaDJ4ko6Ogumt36dorogymiN6mFqVoxtVH_lIz6ilJt3qmwogTl4yFjDH7MX0bnOAnIE0XhDWE_-JLMekgaoJn1WNM1NMiI2P5upUbL9OiN6m2TGZi5eofxs20z4axa-oU6bH09zk2oLLtm3PeuXhQAN2DXF4hvvWSl1vKWYJBLWTd9iL_YrsPkQWSZezgsvLmBPIPkAo70/-S8kF2ikZqJZrnFkaNBndpdYdyvcUsk0/7" target="_blank"&gt;创纪录的奔跑&lt;/a&gt;，&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;这并没有停止黄金。&lt;/strong&gt;由于对全球经济的焦虑，银行仍然对&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/SBmrw6Z7G_c6m765FcCLilGHIla9_3CYwmH-bNsxeA1wWRA2JCLYZt0seaPpb1fZGp4Jp41fg0c0epngeBfe3irmVPPQiMsvG2nzZqhKhY1bdX-sI-lM2kMVUK7ablev97Uzszl7z0YMLDqf1SSTZQwNELGxoet6YHpk4ui6jfhlp7MrWaoleFMt7fvEyzhw7uMZ0hRNBkAsAadNtoOroweW9zIfkNM0tZus178VEzMro0emmCfJIL4sgNsLNmcNq4bUZIIv00ZN-Wjb8k0pastDBIn6uC0ghNctQdUkwo-_1Wmm5EvaipQ_9U27GXpY-_NZmi0rT8ObnJnBo5Y5yBTSU6giHqPfORiIjOHTMRjLSiKwlH13JtJwyQc/xFL-M8ul9feS9xQX_9fb-lTZDFdrrdy9/7" target="_blank"&gt;金条的安全状况&lt;/a&gt;看涨。同时，在政策制定者今天晚些时候开会时，美联储&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/GHTISwrSJkHIlhaEErm4MJlyod0bCu40-RKYBiHV3iQNBaQ7JFD3WZALlatLnsuSbjVmClmGl8T1GhNNVVDK3J6h5A0stm4dYjX0oOVqgYSKy528JY-Qzjs9cw9W0u53fL1bRdPD0kdT3_LLZsTbITRagD0HkLDBOnUT3jliRc9or8aJrQ5vBw9egX6A0sVEgrOLHLs7Hz-l7Hf_kdNcMJec9pSTik3Sl0gpC5nAEVs1yG2-QNIpMf8dkQqThpDNJ7NJon51rkRETqFv8L16xcgqg3Xq6Ym0U90TNNUIaN6Be2ta86DmBWGxywPF-o4Zw46Ult9lJo7BtO8w-x-9BKRkXYYhkj7m8ZfjH3V2vXt9fGhkY3wFDJswaME/pL5-c-NuFjOTsTOA0LDA4AxJNtOnxKOy/7" target="_blank"&gt;有望保持借贷成本稳定&lt;/a&gt;，投资者将重点关注该银行最新的经济预测。获取&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Qbs-BLKeIjE02AJC8IKZ4SIuSFP-UpTXoJTX-ROg84yi1EIB40rQZK82ggNJ8j2kGS_vQw5De5VNrEXoGSu359PnGyJtpdgXQCYoTPIyCqSvOc86levbGP9KKSJ8kz2Zg8_yWzWs_r2Bx9vNao83oWUdyz7IZoYy2b6zzVbpz9sRavIWGdHw6u5U8UZrejbdiOlB0g2YYsALIvA1974MxFRxEzH1biRRJNZFnRp2BGxsuE_5nq3r1QS7HsHg_z3JdYcqTwe9_qT8vbPpWK1X3LLhmTllKyZs3UlHt2Mc2Av9tisjTdsoLAOoQO0jGPhV5z40WHEqoynRXEqYSSFBIwwjY_0ZlP8-pb61OhG4qt4SldUsxZIUDxL16iA/DNh6wqNeIg7BMK2Obbdlv6NXo6dy_KaR/7" target="_blank"&gt;有关市场正在发生的事情的&lt;/a&gt;最新信息。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;当他们今天与特朗普会面时，有十几个石油公司的&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;首席执行官&lt;/strong&gt;将传达感激之情&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/LDWnb5esBzM3QenF8KGRmEfZAZ2jO-5rcBx0N5TYm5Lw3Zy8skhaDHDAclNhH9DBCEXSos57ZaTczq05uXw3Y97KPP3XQdxA9JQAXkU3Om1_W4I8sm2efAqSht0-VVaQtcyC4jQTTUjvesGeOuoEHD5yP9aCT27BBzf_q5HZJzLtZ_T83niwkgXj-85IivcT5cgmQl5g7dJEBuwyM0-eGgMb16FUJr8N__Fi63vdF94oZHbyH9NJqlYTRDG1bY-IYkiIflQHgcPHY6Uiu0FnVz9xf7y1fnHrWtvks_LfUm3DhT5xyuBsiVF78IaArP7H-mD4Ys5rJGqX7gPxsCe119eRrrCJxh9eRYvDoB0m4XwJATDZpRVlxqEjTYo/klToeQjgVaKvx9q3K-vETwe4jvKTSBL0/7" target="_blank"&gt;，并谨慎&lt;/a&gt;。总统是美国石油和天然气生产的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/T_9_UbO6FkKzNIh8wOcIwi37etoduP3k1Ul_rRlMd1aUY-amu1MVWUtxEOEPKvWomf2ZHBDQ1_wQx7oWbhzkP4cdU27DI-6E1uybJBZlzvo95wyb3uGyXy04d4I4Ti3JbH3zDEoLtcDSi4orwbLpHEGPVwH27I4II-E1I6SV8YLDorKggzCx_Wa9N-RquCBj_BRKEhimAYBGsECdzYWai75ikB3QMYQd-hjDUZIL7sZXoXhXsrEObjjYcjQh3_wDMVs7YvYNlg1pqnXBc70EekII8RrASXqW5b-J3WrMwBOQeSTA7Nsrt6tMEV1QRfIpMJXmrl39SPmkQNuEEfW9Jf8YxN00RgQncuiLTAxHKyAGaJ6wsfBK09oc4U4/3bg9bQFZV_RM0KR5YObVYFVT9IG8XTmN/7" target="_blank"&gt;毫不掩饰的冠军&lt;/a&gt;。但是，人们&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/lRXDgH7gLFKz8kD3idYDjcS1gvQLvtgu0ptxfToTjzjrB0PI98sOqJGHWV4MkYEbo5gIbEEkEX5iJOpxB6fu3hlek90wNjFTZgvlp0WY1zyZ_1SHnH9DCxMtbK9mAdSnRQ5pEvRvVX8vjD7D5YWqgE2fiKjfODpK7_QEgs9evwDHVT-rQaAniMUoQ1X1Eyho-O9sbdVUhF8tSb8j20rqKbvuJvoDE4p4nli28kXujh6-24dn2JOzDPBDQRNqZKl_HIN90vysj8vMYC9WD5acV1r0DlKCb9SHCfgYyVWIjfGi96T4QGE8THSBy53ohb5fHDl8Dcj2kYBEoiKLITI6j3Cnek_wfyjAlpAsXY0oTYHYAICAKSvUGFpMNrA/jTa-VXalzfrc1FNb74ZuY8VAzg8t-iuG/7" target="_blank"&gt;对原油价格存在担忧&lt;/a&gt;，特朗普&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ww_Hl-DqA9rGQxc6B6nzyoUFm9AgjGEVlGHl-63FaFUrammTLyBGJDKN7othzxA2ZhxlivqV1tbWpDwLf