mily: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;储蓄目标&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;。此举是Starmer在削减海外发展预算并削减大多数养老金领取的冬季燃油付款之后，Starmer &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Ga8bLikpRBNgewlcrbQ7wKZSUDb5F2En8qmNXp126bjMbvTA4Gb0QNUTXNKmuDAsLZE7spZkGjg9WjEFqR3RwSSWsMlBsGHnKrZ9bB6Kj8qIIZ_QcDI8jpkkQDg_t5T_EZjTZe27_9mKOJjaFbuyNMIj7lHZ0m0BXWVZ2YLw0b3eRsY7wcUl59GJ6oRlRS2B0WfscQHhunAltzmxUwe0Gcuxo14NShnpCcwf2uue_q3lzZT29x4p_wwjmMB0NsVjHZuiqIOybTAz-ApbsuE_wucUUOAwIJx-ulCdhC0AV6ICqXSM_zuOWpOjky0v9FQWHE3z8k_9aki3pT9HofXeZuUbZL1zRB5p6DIUL7J2pLBDT_9Hk67Fe5lriEs/k6KdzQlyFw5sOjcEGwvp432APG2a67Fr/7"&gt;显然处于劳动传统不一致的情况&lt;/a&gt;下的最新例子。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;台湾在年度军事演习中首次将2027年确定&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;为&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/cyupxhVZi8_M0F4m_J7tZ811TEKJB_iQ9zYLQOnCe2FPpsGK0KfW6RbMJVDxUjCEVm_12cO49vjckl6J5EO9wy1ysdcmyYu0JhReLd9-3Q8WAktT4qOfZJP6wc_sCNMHmh6X-mou1iycjOynSVfpF2Ht961vf94vkIOcH8Hv-bof2mh4QGlBdt-buXrGb2n9uGdpHBFWLBpm88-ePLDVYxjgSdziLlSkO0q6xhf2W1Oqfcl1SWvy_-1Zb-58TveQUdujgVrpgVRQ1D6TDkBgfc6bSILOTebWGMnGDNdsL8hwGFEZNx_fLARtFCOsPcYic1O2XIdr2hEoWvQ8FoG_bzz1w2_fNCYF-920MhRwqAH-rRvE6VMtKmL65HU/y53pKr2NqxPpfFKanh9WHZB0D5pIUZkH/7" title="中国入侵的潜在年份"&gt;中国入侵的潜在年份&lt;/a&gt;，因为在自绑的岛屿上担心北京的紧张局势。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i2qrzpHKfafE/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i2qrzpHKfafE/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top